Day which falls on March 8 or Sunday.
</P>
<P>
In a statement issued here Friday, women's affairs standing
committee of the House of People's Representatives of Ethiopia
said the delay in issuing laws pertaining to women's rights has
impeded benefits which members of the fair sex could have savored
otherwise.
</P>
<P>
