3.4 percent in real terms and the per capita net income of rural
residents, 4.6 percent;
</P>
<P>
-- Last year seven million people in cities and towns found
their first jobs and 2.45 million redundant workers were
re-employed; the registered unemployment rate in cities and towns
was 3.1 percent; the natural population growth rate was 1.006
percent;
</P>
<P>
-- Foreign exchange revenues from international tourists
exceeded 12.1 billion US dollars and revenues from domestic
tourists reached 211.3 billion yuan for the year. 
